Domain management.

USAGE:
  scw domain domain <command>

AVAILABLE COMMANDS:
  disable-auto-renew Disable auto renew
  disable-dnssec     Disable a domain's DNSSEC
  enable-auto-renew  Enable auto renew
  enable-dnssec      Update domain DNSSEC
  get                Get domain
  get-auth-code      Get a domain's authorization code
  list               List domains
  list-renewable     List domains that can be renewed
  lock-transfer      Lock the transfer of a domain
  search             Search available domains
  unlock-transfer    Unlock the transfer of a domain
  update             Update a domain's contacts

FLAGS:
  -h, --help                help for domain
      --list-sub-commands   List all subcommands

GLOBAL FLAGS:
  -c, --config string    The path to the config file
  -D, --debug            Enable debug mode
  -o, --output string    Output format: json or human, see 'scw help output' for more info (default "human")
  -p, --profile string   The config profile to use

Use "scw domain domain [command] --help" for more information about a command.
